23
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:51,680
Leave now!

24
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:52,840
Leave now!

25
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,280
Qingqing,

26
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:54,280
Qingqing.

27
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,560
Stop. We are in hospital.

28
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,799
Let go of me!

29
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,719
Kang Shao has been arrested.

30
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,159
Question him anytime.

31
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,400
As for him,

32
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,319
sorry.

33
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:08,280
Leave now!

34
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,280
Yanshu, let go!

35
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,759
Let go!

36
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:16,759
Don't think I didn't see it.

37
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:19,039
You were the one who shot Guan Xingkai.

38
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:21,479
If the Guan family finds out about this,

39
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,840
forget the marriage,

40
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,520
they'll kill you!

41
00:02:27,879 --> 00:02:28,439
Yanshu,

42
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:30,680
I'll make Xingkai change his mind

43
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,800
and return to me.

44
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:33,560
I won't lose to that actress!

45
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,759
Are you insane?

46
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,199
Ma'am.

47
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:51,879
You've disappointed me deeply.

48
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,000
Xingkai.

49
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:37,759
Xingkai.

50
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:42,599
Ma'am.

51
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:48,000
Mother.

52
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:49,199
It's all my fault.

53
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:52,599
If I hadn't forced you
to marry Qingqing,

54
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:55,840
you wouldn't have ended up like this.

55
00:03:56,439 --> 00:03:56,879
Mother,

56
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,280
