221
00:13:33,501 --> 00:13:37,107
♪Glory falls like ashes♪

222
00:13:37,629 --> 00:13:40,943
♪Sleeves flutter♪

223
00:13:41,117 --> 00:13:44,747
♪You sing of love and hate
on high stage♪

224
00:13:45,341 --> 00:13:48,638
♪Yearning brings only sorrow♪

225
00:13:48,925 --> 00:13:53,022
♪But in your eyes, I found resolve♪

226
00:13:55,005 --> 00:13:58,726
♪After one final song of parting♪

227
00:13:58,781 --> 00:14:02,582
♪We'll meet again only through tears♪

